    overview: "Appointment management is one of the most labour-intensive administrative tasks for Riyadh clinics, law firms, consulting practices, and professional service businesses. Patients and clients increasingly prefer WhatsApp for booking — but human receptionists cannot be available around the clock, and missed messages lead to lost appointments and frustrated customers.\n\nElecti's AI Receptionist for Riyadh businesses solves this by handling the entire appointment cycle via WhatsApp: checking real-time calendar availability, booking the appointment, sending an Arabic and English confirmation, delivering automated reminders at 24 and 2 hours before the appointment, and processing rescheduling or cancellations — all without requiring a human receptionist to be involved. The result is fewer missed appointments, reduced no-show rates, and a reception team freed to focus on the in-person experience rather than phone and WhatsApp administration.",
